n="0836b07" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0836b07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000035943">資州</placeName>山北蘭若<persName key="A010342">處寂</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0836b08"/><persName key="A010342">釋處寂</persName>，俗姓<name>周</name>氏<ptr target="#n2590"/>，<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>人也。師事<persName key="A018081">寶修禪師</persName><ptr target="#n2591"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b09"/>服勤<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g837"/>寡慾，與物無競。雅通玄奧，居山北，行<lb
ed="T" n="0836b10"/>杜多行。<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>聞焉，詔入內，賜摩納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1327"/>僧伽梨，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b11"/>辭乞歸山。涉四十年<ptr target="#n2592"/>，足不到聚落。坐一胡<lb
ed="T" n="0836b12"/>床，宴默不寐。常有虎蹲伏座下，如家畜類。<lb
ed="T" n="0836b13"/><placeName key="PL000000035943">資</placeName>民所重，學其道者臻萃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1405"/>。由是頗形奇異，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b14"/>如：<persName key="A010305">無相<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>自<placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅國</placeName>將來謁<persName key="A018081">詵<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，<persName key="A010342">寂</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0836b15"/>預誡眾曰：「外來之賓明日當見矣。宜灑掃<lb
ed="T" n="0836b16"/>以待之。」明日，果有海東賓至也。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371984406" notAfter-iso="+0721-01-07"><name>開元</name>初</date>，新<lb
ed="T" n="0836b17"/>除太守<persName key="A012484">王曄</persName>──本黃冠也，<date notBefore-iso="+0710-08-23" key="j19806161981175" notAfter-iso="+0712-03-04"><name>景雲</name>中</date>曾立少功<ptr target="#n2593"/>──，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b18"/><anchor xml:id="beg0836003"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0836003"/>于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000035943">是郡</ref>，終於<name>釋</name>子苞藏禍心。上任處<lb
ed="T" n="0836b19"/>分，令境內應是沙門追集<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1728"/>。唯<persName key="A010342">寂</persName>久不下山，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b20"/>或勸<persName key="A010342">寂</persName>往參，免為厲階<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1729"/>。<persName key="A010342">寂</persName>謂弟子曰：「汝雖<lb
ed="T" n="0836b21"/>出家，猶未識業，<ref type="person" target="#A010342">吾</ref>之未死，<persName key="A012484">王曄</persName>其如<ref type="person" target="#A010342">吾</ref>何？」<lb
ed="T" n="0836b22"/>迨乎<persName key="A012484">王<roleName>公</roleName></persName>上官三日，緇徒畢至。或曰：「唯<persName key="A010342">處寂</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0836b23"/>蔑視<ref type="person" target="#A012484">藩侯</ref>，弗來致賀。」<persName key="A012484">曄</persName>微怒也，屈諸僧，升<lb
ed="T" n="0836b24"/><anchor xml:id="beg0836sgsz11"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>聽</sic><corr>廳</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0836sgsz11"/>坐已，將啟怒端，問<persName key="A010342">寂</persName>違拒之由，慍色悖<lb
ed="T" n="0836b25"/>興，僧皆股<anchor xml:id="beg0836004"/>慄<anchor xml:id="end0836004"/>。<persName key="A012484">曄</persName>俄然仆地，左右扶掖歸宅，<lb
ed="T" n="0836b26"/>至廳事<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1730"/>後屏樹，如被摑頰之聲，禺中<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1731"/>氣絕。<lb
ed="T" n="0836b27"/>自此人謂為妄欲加諸道人，一至於此。<persName key="A010342">寂</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0836b28"/>以<date from-iso="+0734-02-13" key="j19891911989219" to-iso="+0734-03-13"><name>開元</name>二十二年正月</date>示滅，享年八十七<ptr target="#n2594"/>。<placeName key="PL000000035943">資<lb
ed="T" n="0836b29"/>中</placeName>至今崇仰焉。</p>
